title: 820-3332 Backlight issue
message:
I'm trying to diagnose a no backlight on a 2012 15" Macbook.

When I measure voltage on pin 3 of q9706 the backlight turns on, as soon as I take the multimeter off pin 3 of q9706 the backlight turns off again.

Should I replace q9706 ?

title: 820-3332 Backlight issue
message:
Q9706 Pin 3 .98v, Pin 4 11.7v and 0v on 1,2,5,6

Q9707 Pin 2 0.7v,  Pin 3 3.24v and 0v on 1,4,5,6.
